snippet.title: Parallel - Alpha Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Parallel is a futuristic racing game that takes place on colonized distant planets, jumping between timelines to out-speed your opponents. Step in your racing machine and become the fastest of all time with the game's unique double-thruster gameplay.

Parallel is available on itch.io!
https://igad.itch.io/runningoutontime

This project is a collaborative effort of Team Zero One, a group of students at the Breda University of Applied Sciences.

#IndieGames #RacingGames #Parallel

Music:
Bounce Off - Solvence     (Licensed through EpidemicSound)
